  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buy the First Turnip Boy Game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/33e2177844ebd6c82f5ce27f0b16cdf6.poster.avif?t=1758386170\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/33e2177844ebd6c82f5ce27f0b16cdf6.webm?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/33e2177844ebd6c82f5ce27f0b16cdf6.mp4?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Turnip Boy is ready to commit more felonies in this comedic action-adventure game with roguelite elements.</strong> This time the career criminal is teaming up with the fearsome Pickled Gang to plan and execute the weirdest heist of all time! Shake down hostages, steal precious valuables, and explore the deep, dark depths and history of the Botanical Bank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/953508ccad89818b5e5c0af0056eedd4.avif?t=1758386170\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A thrilling single-player adventure full of bank robbing, dark web browsing, and fuzz fighting!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/b7f2b7a276ed985429f267dedc22f04a.poster.avif?t=1758386170\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/b7f2b7a276ed985429f267dedc22f04a.webm?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/b7f2b7a276ed985429f267dedc22f04a.mp4?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelite elements to turnip the action.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/6312d4d647b1719c713b98e1117cdc86.poster.avif?t=1758386170\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/6312d4d647b1719c713b98e1117cdc86.webm?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An array of wacky weapons!</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/235fbfe15ce1f9b81eea42111cdfc0ef.poster.avif?t=1758386170\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/235fbfe15ce1f9b81eea42111cdfc0ef.webm?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take on whoever the bank throws at you in intense shootouts, from security guards to elite veggie swat teams!</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/0654a568136a7eb86221cfc1cd17ee63.poster.avif?t=1758386170\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097230/extras/0654a568136a7eb86221cfc1cd17ee63.webm?t=1758386170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Earn collectable hats to wear, new banger tracks to blast, and discover a deeper history of Turnip Boy’s world and how it came to be!</p>",
